  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "body": "Tong was the mayor of the ${link_0} town of ${link_1}. He loved to glorify his town's former leader, ${link_2} the Great, just as much as he loved to denounce the ${link_3}. He used his own brand of justice (\"just-us\"), which placed any defendants at a severe disadvantage as he alone acted as judge, jury, and prosecution.",
