      "section": [
        "Tong"
      ],
      "text": "Tong was the mayor of the Earth Kingdom town of Chin Village. He loved to glorify his town's former leader, Chin the Great, just as much as he loved to denounce the Avatar. He used his own brand of justice (\"just-us\"), which placed any defendants at a severe disadvantage as he alone acted as judge, jury, and prosecution."
    },
    {
      "body": "During an ${link_0}, ${link_1} revealed himself as the Avatar, only to be arrested. While the Avatar was in his ${link_2}, Mayor Tong explained to him that \"Avatar Day\" was formed after Avatar ${link_3} killed the village's leader, Chin the Great.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Avatar Day festival",
          "key": "${link_0}",
          "target": {
